  <prompt>
    Extend `PlaybookEmbeddingService.cs:28-30` embed-input composition to include `documentTypes + intents + triggerPhrases` from `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata` (the JSON field added in task 031). The augmented embed-input becomes: `playbookName + description + triggerPhrases + tags + documentTypes + intents + jpsTriggerPhrases`. Implements spec FR-10.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform BFF developer. Expert in `PlaybookEmbeddingService` + Azure AI Search embedding ingestion + ADR-013 facade discipline.</role>

  <goal>
    `PlaybookEmbeddingService` composes embed input from existing 4 sources PLUS 3 new fields read from `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata` JSON. Unit test verifies the composed string. Integration smoke (warm tier) confirms a re-indexed playbook with `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata.documentTypes = ["nda"]` plus `triggerPhrases = ["summarize this NDA"]` becomes searchable via "summarize this NDA" query (full benchmark in task 038).
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec FR-10 + design.md WP1.5. Current state at `PlaybookEmbeddingService.cs:28-30` is `playbookName + description + triggerPhrases + tags`. The new field `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata` is JSON; the service must JSON-parse it tolerantly (treat malformed JSON as "no extra signal" rather than failing) and append its `documentTypes + intents + triggerPhrases` arrays to the embed input string.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PlaybookEmbedding/PlaybookEmbeddingService.cs</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/architecture/jpsmatchingmetadata-schema.json</file>
      <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/PlaybookEmbedding/</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Stay inside `Services/Ai/` boundary — embedding service is AI-internal; CRUD code must consume via PublicContracts facade only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Per-task BFF publish-size measurement; report delta vs Phase 2 baseline.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-10 acceptance: search for "summarize this NDA" returns Summarize-NDA top-1 on 100-doc benchmark (task 038 validates with real data).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">JSON parse must be tolerant — null / malformed `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata` falls back to existing 4-source composition (no breaking change for un-backfilled playbooks).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">CLAUDE.md §10 test obligation — add unit tests under `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/PlaybookEmbedding/`.</constraint>
  </constraints>

